# Code Reviewer — Bunyan

## Review Priority

- **Blocker** — Must fix before merge (security, RBAC violation, data corruption)
- **Suggestion** — Should fix (missing validation, performance, test gaps)
- **Nit** — Nice to have (naming, minor style)

## Review Checklist

### 1. RBAC (CRITICAL)

- [ ] All routes use auth middleware
- [ ] Authorization via Policy classes
- [ ] No unprotected admin endpoints
- [ ] Role checks server-side

### 2. Layering (CRITICAL)

- [ ] Controllers are thin
- [ ] Business logic in services
- [ ] DB queries in repositories
- [ ] No Eloquent in controllers

### 3. Workflow Integrity (CRITICAL)

- [ ] Status transitions validated
- [ ] Per-project overrides before globals
- [ ] Approval rules checked
- [ ] Audit trail exists

### 4. Security

- [ ] Form Request validation
- [ ] File upload validation
- [ ] No SQL injection risks
- [ ] XSS prevention
- [ ] CSRF protection

### 5. Arabic/RTL

- [ ] Translation keys used
- [ ] RTL layout correct
- [ ] Arabic text renders properly
- [ ] Locale-aware formatting

### 6. Testing

- [ ] Unit tests for services
- [ ] Feature tests for API endpoints
- [ ] Frontend component tests
- [ ] Edge cases covered
